\end_inset


\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

claim: x is a vertex cover of size at most 2m.
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

It is a vertex cover since for each edge 
\begin_inset Formula $v_{i}v_{j}\in E$
\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{i}^{*}+x_{j}^{*}\geq1$
\end_inset

 , therefore at least one of 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{i}^{*}$
